 \"from\": 828, \"to\": 852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to a crowd of 200,000, more than 5.9 million television viewers watched rapper Jul light up the cauldron in an atmosphere worthy of a Marseille football match.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 1026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1001, \"end\": 1010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.9999999918809408, \"rank\": 8.119039672068749e-09, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"a crowd\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 5.9 million television viewers\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 930}, {\"ngram\": \"rapper Jul\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"the cauldron\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"an atmosphere\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That in itself was a massive relief to the organisers who then watched as the torch began its journey, the public turning out in huge numbers along the way.\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a massive relief\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisers\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1081}, {\"ngram\": \"the torch\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"its journey\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"huge numbers\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nearly 1.2 million people are estimated to have turned out to watch the relay, with many families on the roads in an atmosphere worthy of the Tour de France.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1328, \"end\": 1342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999694383000061, \"rank\": 2.93738083036283e-05, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nearly 1.2 million people\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"the relay\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"many families\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"the roads\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"an atmosphere\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been accompanied every step of the way, however, by a procession of 200 police officers, and security remains a concern.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"a procession\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"200 police officers\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"a concern\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The torch has, as the authorities feared, attracted its share of protesters, but they were largely muted during the first month.\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The torch\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1483}, {\"ngram\": \"the authorities\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ngram\": \"its share\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1535}, {\"ngram\": \"protesters\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1549}, {\"ngram\": \"the first month\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Tuesday, Interior Minister Gerald Darmanin reported that 81 arrests had been made and 145 actions aimed at disrupting the relay had been prevented since May 8.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1616, \"end\": 1633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\", \"score\": 0.9916449612599049, \"rank\": 0.004861972823072897, \"text\": \"Interior Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wik