"ngram\": \"discontent\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"a stereotypical shrug\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"the shoulders\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's very French what's going on,\\\" says David Lazarus, the mayor of Chambly (DVG) in the Oise region, north-west of Paris.\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2069, \"end\": 2082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lazarus\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Lazarus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lazarus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lazarus\"}, {\"begin\": 2145, \"end\": 2150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.559807210913209e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mayor\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2093}, {\"ngram\": \"Chambly\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"DVG\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"the Oise region\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"north-west\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We criticise a lot in advance, and in fact we do not properly gauge the popular dimension of these Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2172}, {\"ngram\": \"advance\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2183}, {\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"the popular dimension\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2243}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Protesters or not, the torch continues its journey across the country, even finding time to mingle with the stars of cinema as it was walked up th